---
// Journey.astro
---
<section class="journey-panel">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-24">
      <div class="content-left">
        <h3 class="heading">
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>When you lean in and</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>step into the</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>transformation journey,</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>deeply-rooted change happens.</span></span>
        </h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-right">
        <p class="paragraph">
          <strong>AT THE CENTER</strong> of who we are as an organization is <strong>JESUS CHRIST</strong>, who holds the power for genuine transformation. Our values, principles and strategies are rooted in biblical truth.
        </p>
        <p class="paragraph">
          <strong>AT VANGUARD</strong>, we believe that we are His vessels. We have a responsibility to pour out into the lives of others because God has already poured out into our own hearts.
        </p>
        <blockquote class="scripture">
          “For we are His workmanship, created in Christ Jesus for good works, which God prepared beforehand that we should walk in them.”
          <br>
          <span class="reference">- Ephesians 2:10</span>
        </blockquote>
        <a href="#team" class="button">More About Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .journey-panel {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-grey);
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .content-left {
    grid-column: 2 / 24;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content-left {
      grid-column: 4 / 12;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }

  .heading {
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .heading {
      font-size: 4.8rem;
    }
  }

  .content-right {
    grid-column: 2 / 24;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content-right {
      grid-column: 14 / 22;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .paragraph {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .scripture {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-taupe);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-taupe);
    margin: 4rem 0;
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .reference {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    background-color: var(--color-grey);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 4rem;
    transition: all 0.3s var(--ease-out-cubic);
  }

  .button:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-black);
  }
</style>
